==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Discontinuer
<hw>Dis`con*tin"u*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
discontinues, or breaks off or away from; an absentee.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He was no gadder abroad, not <qex>discontinuer</qex> from his
convent for a long time.</q> <rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Discontinuity</ent>⟦br⟧
